data.description: Step back to the elegance and grace of this 19th Century Victorian beauty with so much charm you won’t want to leave! Beautiful hardwood floors,  high ceilings and a fireplace .  This home has  the perfect combination of preserving the old while updating the essentials. You'll love the kitchen with wood plank ceiling a 1st floor laundry and full bath.   2nd floor features 4 bedrooms and 1 full baths.  Some antique lighting remain.  Generous deck overlooks private fenced in back yard with a two car garage.  Here's your chance to own the first house that was built on Chambers Avenue!
